OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMainly fine, but with low cloud
OL,6,Fin some southern and western areas,
OL,7,Fand with a humid feel generally.
OL,8,FBecoming hot in developing sunny
OL,9,Fperiods, perhaps triggering isolated
OL,10,Fthundery showers.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FClear skies at first before
OL,13,Fcloud in the west spreads eastwards
OL,14,Facross the region by the morning.
OL,15,FWinds becoming moderate and breezy
OL,16,Falong the coast by the morning.
OL,17,
OL,18,CSaturday:FCloudy at first with some
OL,19,Fsunny spells later in the day. Winds
OL,20,Fgradually easing during the afternoon
OL,21,Fand feeling a little less hot.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
